descriptionHtml:
Are you a wanderer who is planning to Travel to Rosario or an escapist who wants to pay a virtual tour on maps? Interested in its people, culture, art, history, cuisine, flora and fauna? Want to get complete Guide for the exquisite places of Rosario like Plaza Sarmiento, Monumento a la Bandera (Flag Monument), Teatro El Circulo, Parque Nacional a la Bandera, La Isla de los Inventos, Parque Independencia, Parque de Espana, City Center Rosario Casino, Parque Urquiza, Museo de los Ninos. Want to speak like a native in Spanish or plan your route on the map? If yes, then this Rosario Travel & Explore app is just for you!

All features and images in Rosario City Guide are available offline. This Rosario Travel App is for the globetrotters who go by the quote, “All journeys have secret destinations of which the traveler is unaware”. With Rosario Tourist Guide, Unveil the Veiled places, Connect with plethora of people, understand culture, art and history, Speak with natives in their language, relish the authentic food and take delight in the festivities.

Apart from this, Rosario Travel & Explore guides you Why, When and How to visit various places in Rosario with precise location on the detailed Map. There are two ways to explore this app - Category view and EduBank favorite places view. Pin your destinations and get the routes on the Map. Not only this, you can see exactly how the places look like with Street View integrated in this app. The app also has a feature to Rate and write Review/Experience regarding entity(s) through Login. Your Travel experience and rating will help the user community.

Rosario Travel Guide is divided into the following categories:-

*Art & History Aficionados
*Carnivals & Festivals
*Nature Nomads
*Spiritual Sanctuaries
*Wildlife Wanderings
*Celebrities Cells
*Business Boulevards
*Transportation Hubs
*Cuisine
*Routes
*Commemorative Events
*Entertainment
*Flora
*Fauna
*Sports
*Geo & Socio Outlook
*What's News
*Lingo Sense
*Facts
*Educational Excellence

Main Features of Rosario City Guide are:-

* The app works offline. No internet connection needed to Explore!
* Routes not only take you to the destinations but show other fascinating places also.
* Separate section for main Attractions!
* Informs about Airways, Roadways, Railways and Waterways for a hassle free Travel.
* Rove through the Wildlife Wanderings!
* Not only taste but learn to cook mouth-watering delicacies.
* Get updated with live news!
* EduBank is here to save all your favorite entities!
* A phrasebook to learn the basic Spanish phrases.
* Know facts from the factfile pop-ups!
* Communicate in the City from your own Language!

Rosario Travel & Explore is all that you need to Travel in Rosario. The virtual trip is so mesmerizing that you will go for the real one!

We make SMARTY apps, “Simple Masterly Approach to Refine Thinking" for YOU.
